commits.content:
$primary-index: 500;
$primary2-index: 500;
$primary3-index: 700;
$secondary-index: 800;
$secondary2-index: 500;
$secondary3-index: 500;
$background-index: 500;
$forground-index: 50;
$warn_index: A700;

$venues_mat_primary: (50: #e1f5fd,
  100: #b3e5fa,
  200: #82d5f7,
  300: #51c4f3,
  400: #2db7f2,
  500: #0aaaf0,
  600: #069ce1,
  700: #BCB5C7,
  800: #0178b9,
  900: #005898,
  contrast: (50: $black-87-opacity,
    100: $black-87-opacity,
    200: $black-87-opacity,
    300: $black-87-opacity,
    400: $black-87-opacity,
    500: white,
    600: white,
    700: white,
    800: white,
    900: white,
  ),
);

$venues_mat_primary2: (50: #dedbfb,
  100: #c8c4f9,
  200: #b3adf7,
  300: #9e95f5,
  400: #887ef2,
  500: #7367F0,
  600: #5e50ee,
  700: #4839eb,
  800: #3321e9,
  900: #2716db,
  A100: #f3f2fe,
  A200: #ffffff,
  A400: #ffffff,
  A700: #2313c4,
  contrast: (50: $black-87-opacity,
    100: $black-87-opacity,
    200: $black-87-opacity,
    300: $black-87-opacity,
    400: $black-87-opacity,
    500: white,
    600: white,
    700: white,
    800: white,
    900: white,
  ),
);

$venues_mat_accent: (50: #e3f1fa,
  100: #baddf5,
  200: #8fc8ee,
  300: #64b2e7,
  400: #43a2e4,
  500: #2093e0,
  600: #1785d3,
  700: #0a74c1,
  800: #0063af,
  900: #004690,
  contrast: (50: $black-87-opacity,
    100: $black-87-opacity,
    200: $black-87-opacity,
    300: $black-87-opacity,
    400: $black-87-opacity,
    500: white,
    600: white,
    700: white,
    800: white,
    900: white,
  ),
);

$venues_mat_accent2: (
  500: #777777,
  contrast: (
    500: $black-87-opacity
  )
);

$venue_mat_accent3: (
  50: #ffffff,
  100: #ffffff,
  200: #ffffff,
  300: #ffffff,
  400: #fafafa,
  500: #ededed,
  600: #e0e0e0,
  700: #d3d3d3,
  800: #c7c7c7,
  900: #bababa,
  contrast: (
    50: $black-87-opacity,
    100: $black-87-opacity,
    200: $black-87-opacity,
    300: $black-87-opacity,
    400: $black-87-opacity,
    500: $black-87-opacity,
    600: $black-87-opacity,
    700: $black-87-opacity,
    800: $black-87-opacity,
    900: $black-87-opacity,
  ),
);

$venues_mat_warn-1: (
  50: #ff3056,
  100: #ff1741,
  200: #fc002e,
  300: #e30029,
  400: #c90025,
  500: #b00020,
  600: #96001b,
  700: #7d0017,
  800: #630012,
  900: #4a000d,
  contrast: (50: $black-87-opacity,
    100: $black-87-opacity,
    200: $black-87-opacity,
    300: $black-87-opacity,
    400: $black-87-opacity,
    500: white,
    600: white,
    700: white,
    800: white,
    900: white,
  ),
);

$venues_mat_warn: (50: #ffebee,
  100: #ffcdd2,
  200: #ef9a9a,
  300: #e57373,
  400: #ef5350,
  500: #f44336,
  600: #e53935,
  700: #d32f2f,
  800: #c62828,
  900: #b71c1c,
  A100: #ff8a80,
  A200: #ff5252,
  A400: #ff1744,
  A700: #b00020,
  contrast: (50: $black-87-opacity,
    100: $black-87-opacity,
    200: $black-87-opacity,
    300: $black-87-opacity,
    400: $black-87-opacity,
    500: white,
    600: white,
    700: white,
    800: $white-87-opacity,
    900: $white-87-opacity,
    A100: $black-87-opacity,
    A200: white,
    A400: white,
    A700: white,
  ));

$venues_mat_background : (50: #ffffff,
  100: #ffffff,
  200: #ffffff,
  300: #ffffff,
  400: #ffffff,
  500: #F8F8F8,
  600: #ebebeb,
  700: #dedede,
  800: #d2d2d2,
  900: #c5c5c5,
  A100: #ffffff,
  A200: #ffffff,
  A400: #ffffff,
  A700: #b8b8b8,
  contrast: (50: $black-87-opacity,
    100: $black-87-opacity,
    200: $black-87-opacity,
    300: $black-87-opacity,
    400: $black-87-opacity,
    500: #171717,
    600: #171717,
    700: #171717,
    800: #171717,
    900: #171717,
  ),
);

$venue_mat_forground : (50: #171717,
  contrast: (50: white));

$mat-warning : (50: #FE9705,
  contrast: (50: white));

$notifications-theme: ( // default: #FFFFFF,
  info: mat-color(mat-palette($mat-blue), 400),
  success: mat-color(mat-palette($mat-green), 400),
  warning: mat-color(mat-palette($mat-warning), 50),
  danger: mat-color(mat-palette($mat-red), 400),
  idle: map-get($venues_mat_primary2, $primary2-index));

$primary: map-get($venues_mat_primary, $primary3-index);
$primary2: map-get($venues_mat_primary2, $primary2-index);
$primary2-5-opacity: rgba($primary2, 0.5);
$secondary: map-get($venues_mat_accent, $secondary-index);
$secondary2: map-get($venues_mat_accent2, $secondary2-index);
$secondary3: map-get($venue_mat_accent3, $secondary3-index);
$background: map-get($venues_mat_background, $background-index);
$warn: map-get($map: $venues_mat_warn, $key: $warn_index);
$forground: map-get($venue_mat_forground, $forground-index);
$info: map-get($map: $notifications-theme, $key: info);
$success: map-get($map: $notifications-theme, $key: success);
$success-5-opacity: rgba($success, 0.5);
$warning: map-get($map: $notifications-theme, $key: warning);
$danger: map-get($map: $notifications-theme, $key: danger);
$idle: map-get($map: $notifications-theme, $key: idle);
$danger-5-opacity: rgba($danger, 0.5);

$dark: #000000;
$black: #000000;
$white: #ffffff;
$bronze:#AF5F00;
$gold:#FFBD59;
$silver:#676767;
$light-primary: #D9E8F3;
$purple:#9428C7;
